# MJ_odd_or_even

A tiny, dependency-free Python library to check whether an integer is odd or even.

## Installation

```bash
pip install mj_odd_or_even

```python
from mj_odd_or_even import is_odd, is_even

print(is_odd(7))   # True
print(is_even(8))  # True

